SumeetGenderMaleLanguage(s)HindiOriginMeaning

1. Good friend

2. Well pleased

Region of originIndiaOther namesAlternative spellingSumit

Sumeet or Sumit is a masculine given name. It originated from Devanagari language and means "good friend" or "well pleased".[1][2]

Notable people
